title: Top 10 disappointments & NFC East debate
itunes:title: Top 10 disappointments & NFC East debate
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news and discuss Top 10 disappointments so far this season. Plus, the newest hero Conor Orr joins the program to discuss the Giants and the rest of the NFC East.
